.env                ← Your Groq API key — the most important one, NEVER push this
__pycache__/        ← Python auto-generated bytecode, not needed
*.py[cod]           ← Compiled Python files
.venv/ venv/        ← Your virtual environment (huge folder, no need in git)
*.log               ← Log files, just noise in git
.DS_Store           ← Mac OS auto-creates this, useless
.vscode/ .idea/     ← Your editor settings, personal to you